        {
            "title": "歐霸｜曼聯7 ：1淘汰畢爾包 與熱刺齊躋身決賽 將上演英超內訌",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a210997951fdc70c7109725085d9baf9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050905094487429.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>歐霸4強次回合，兩支英超球隊曼聯與熱刺均淘汰對手，決賽將於畢爾包聖馬梅斯球場爭奪冠軍。\n\n</p><h2>曼聯下半場狂入4球</h2>\n<p>曼聯在首回合作客3:0輕取畢爾包，今場回師主場奧脫福球場。比賽初段，16分鐘加拿祖接應傳送推入禁區，惜被對方門將沒收皮球。比賽至31分鐘，畢爾包中場華雷西札爾（Mikel Jauregizar）禁區外起腳，皮球死角破網，在客場追回一球。完半場前，加拿祖射門柱邊出界。\n\n</p>\n<p>下半場曼聯全力反擊，72分鐘，美臣蒙特（Mason Mount）接應（Leny Olivier Yoro）的傳送，在禁區內轉身射入，曼聯將比分送成 1 ：1 。至80分鐘，卡斯美路(Casemiro)接應般如費蘭迪斯（Bruno Fernandes) 的罰球頂入，曼聯反先 2：1 。85分，前鋒賀隆特接應迪亞路的右路傳送撞射入網。補時階段，美臣蒙特把握對方門將解圍的失誤，在半場位置起腳射入，最終曼聯以總比分7：1 淘汰畢爾包躋身決賽。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238210/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"熱刺躋身決賽。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c0a611c555557a7d5f28c781e505ab6d/2025-05/2025-05-08T203037Z_1275175663_UP1EL581KZ0V4_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-BOD-TOT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺躋身決賽。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238211/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼聯總比分 7:1 淘汰畢爾包。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2a84d667565a1e0f3884016b4cf743f4/2025-05/2025-05-08T203149Z_314156890_MT1PRA80037955_RTRMADP_3_PA-IMAGES.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯總比分 7:1 淘汰畢爾包。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238212/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"熱刺今場攻入兩球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7f22408fb7cd6edc8328d8808712be0/2025-05/2025-05-08T203304Z_2113489436_UP1EL581L33VC_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-BOD-TOT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺今場攻入兩球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238213/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"蘇蘭基及柏度樸路今仗均有入球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/21d609b8608b584ea6d55be28bccc835/2025-05/2025-05-08T203455Z_1584630757_UP1EL581L66VJ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-BOD-TOT-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蘇蘭基及柏度樸路今仗均有入球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4238214/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"曼聯下半場攻入四球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c3e152e24b6566251ed1feec33af7fb/2025-05/2025-05-08T204732Z_1949151442_MT1SIPA000ITUS49_RTRMADP_3_SIPA-USA.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯下半場攻入四球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>另一場四強次回合比賽，熱刺首回合贏 3 ：1後，作客波杜基林特。雙方上半場互無紀錄。下半場63分鐘，蘇蘭基（Dominic <b>Solanke</b>）接應羅美路傳送射入。6分鐘後，柏度樸路（Pedro Porro）再入一球，最終熱刺總比數 5 ：1 躋身決賽，將與曼聯爭奪冠軍。\n\n</p>\n<p>歐霸決賽將於香港時間5月22日凌晨4時上演，勝方將獲得來季歐聯資格。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068000/即時-體育-歐霸-曼聯7-1淘汰畢爾包-與熱刺齊躋身決賽-將上演英超內訌",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 05:21:09",
